16:10.667 --> 16:14.290
all the time, the work class is in the bakery? In the 
bakery and... In the court. Carpentry and... In

16:17.954 --> 16:18.435
the court. In the what? In the court. Court? What 
does the court give you? Work. Work in the county.

16:27.284 --> 16:30.647
The same, carpentry, cleaning, and... Several 
jobs, a little bit. I know a little bit of

16:33.616 --> 16:35.959
everything. I'm also a plumber.

16:40.443 --> 16:42.625
Because I've liked learning a little bit of 
everything. Yes. But my profession is a baker. A

16:46.870 --> 16:47.590
baker, yes. Because I worked in Hebron. In 1932, I 
worked in the bakery. Were you married to my uncle?

16:58.601 --> 16:58.661
No. He didn't get married until 1945.

