And for what reason did you never come back to 
Mexico? Well, I had a good time here. My parents

17:12.577 --> 17:17.145
were close by in Camargo. So... Working here is 
good. But I liked it better here. So you come here

17:21.513 --> 17:24.939
and live well. My husband died at the age of 79. He 
didn't go to jail. That's

17:29.420 --> 17:58.768
what I,

17:29.420 --> 17:58.768
you know, I work in the hospital.

17:59.035 --> 18:04.303
We're very interested in health and longevity. 
