19:42.007 --> 19:59.982
primitive societies, anybody who survived 
infancy and then you bring in children, men have no

19:42.007 --> 19:59.982
warfare, which is fairly typical of most. And 
there does seem

20:00.181 --> 20:10.314
to be a very strong genetic component. My father 
was 79. The only reason he died young at 79 is that he

20:11.295 --> 20:16.201
drank a lot. That's true. You drink yourself to 
death at 79. His sister died. When did my aunt

20:22.328 --> 20:26.053
Felipa die? My aunt Felipa died last year. She was 
100 years old. for his older sister.

