38:29.457 --> 38:31.780
only way I can see it. Some people have it, and some 
people... It's an inner drive. I don't know. I

38:36.466 --> 38:36.786
don't know. We always tell her that we think that we 
all inherited from her. But... Because I see it in

38:40.650 --> 38:44.575
school children. There are some parents that just 
