39:49.319 --> 39:53.425
could have done. We had to do it practically on our 
own. Of course, it was her drive. I think because, I

39:58.693 --> 40:02.258
don't know, and daddy was very willing to go along 
with her idea. How much of the year was he usually

40:05.811 --> 40:07.754
gone? Oh, I would say not more than six months. 
