40:16.325 --> 40:20.271
communication was very little. And so he had to 
come and see his family pretty often. Or else, you

40:24.737 --> 40:28.282
know, a whole year would go by and he really 
wouldn't know. So he tried to make it. I wouldn't

40:29.884 --> 40:31.907
say that he'd be gone more than six months. Three to 
six months. And your mother never would go and take

40:34.597 --> 40:37.040
you? Never. She probably went. Well, in fact, I 
think she went until the older ones were ready to

40:39.582 --> 40:45.349
start school. She followed him. My oldest sister, 
my grandmother, took her in so she wouldn't miss.

40:50.474 --> 40:56.500
And then as soon as my oldest brother was old enough 
to go to school, then she stayed. And from then on,

40:56.520 --> 40:58.222
it was a family stay. Father went. But we were 
never, the family was never, now I could say I went

41:01.722 --> 41:08.214
one year, but that was because I wanted to go. I 
wanted to see what it was like. And I went my junior

41:10.919 --> 41:15.387
year in high school. That's when I went to try it. We 
